            <fr:title text="Retract">Retract</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-0025.agda" type="external">erct-0025.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>When <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\colon  A\to  B]]></fr:tex> is a section of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex>, we say that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is a <html:em><html:strong>retract</html:strong></html:em> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>
                <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
              <fr:day>22</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-0023</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0023.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Path object structure on sections"><fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0010.xml" title="Path object" addr="forest://erct/erct-0010" type="local">Path object</fr:link> structure on <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000Y.xml" title="Section-retraction pair" addr="forest://erct/erct-000Y" type="local">sections</fr:link></fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Corollary</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-0023.agda" type="external">erct-0023.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>A suitable <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0010.xml" title="Path object" addr="forest://erct/erct-0010" type="local">path object</fr:link> on <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000Y.xml" title="Section-retraction pair" addr="forest://erct/erct-000Y" type="local">sections</fr:link> to a fixed function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex> is given by a <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0036.xml" title="Contravariant sum of right-cloven families of path objects" addr="forest://erct/erct-0036" type="local">contravariant sum of path objects</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen s:\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen s:\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen s:\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \int _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen s:\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}\mathord {\vartriangle }A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}r\circ  s \sim  1_{B}]]></fr:tex>, as sectionhood witnesses form a <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0032.xml" title="Right cleaving of a family of path objects" addr="forest://erct/erct-0032" type="local">right-cloven family</fr:link> over their underlying sections (<fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001Y.xml" title="The standard cleaving for sectionhood witnesses" addr="forest://erct/erct-001Y" type="local">Example <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-001Y" /></fr:link>). In particular, an isomorphism of sections of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r]]></fr:tex> from 
 <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left \lparen s,h\right \rparen \mathclose {}]]></fr:tex>
 to 
 <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left \lparen s',h'\right \rparen \mathclose {}]]></fr:tex>
 is given by a homotopy <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H_s \colon  s \sim  s']]></fr:tex> together with a higher homotopy <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H_h \colon  h \sim  
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen \lambda {x}\mathpunct {.}\mathsf {act}_{r}
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen H_s x\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\cdot  h'x\right \rparen \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>
                <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
              <fr:day>20</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-001K</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001K.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Contractible types are propositions"><fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001H" type="local">Contractible</fr:link> types are <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link></fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001K.agda" type="external">erct-001K.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>If a type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link>, then it is a <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>20</fr:day></fr:date><fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-001K/0</fr:addr><fr:route>http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001K/0.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
  <html:p>As <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> with some centre <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a:A]]></fr:tex>, we have for any <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x,y:A]]></fr:tex> identifications <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\chi _x \colon  a = x]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\chi _y\colon  a = y]]></fr:tex>. Therefore, we identify <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x]]></fr:tex> with <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[y]]></fr:tex> using <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\chi _x^{-1} \cdot  \chi _y]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
</fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>
                <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
              <fr:day>20</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-001Q</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001Q.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Fiber">Fiber</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001Q.agda" type="external">erct-001Q.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>The <html:em><html:strong>fiber</html:strong></html:em> of a function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex> at an element <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b:B]]></fr:tex> is the type consisting of elements <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\colon  A]]></fr:tex> equipped with identifications <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p\colon  fa=b]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>
                <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
              <fr:day>20</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-001T</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001T.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="n-truncated map"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span> map</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001T.agda" type="external">erct-001T.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>A function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex> is called <html:em><html:strong><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></html:strong></html:em> when all of its <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001Q.xml" title="Fiber" addr="forest://erct/erct-001Q" type="local">fibers</fr:link> are <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001G.xml" title="n-truncated type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span> types</fr:link>. By analogy, we shall also refer to maps as <html:em><html:strong>contractible</html:strong></html:em> when their fibers are; we shall refer to maps as <html:em><html:strong>propositional</html:strong></html:em> when their fibers are <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link>.</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>
                <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
              <fr:day>20</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-001I</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Proposition">Proposition</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001I.agda" type="external">erct-001I.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>A type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is said to be a <html:em><html:strong>proposition</html:strong></html:em> when every <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x:A]]></fr:tex>, the type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible with centre</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x]]></fr:tex>, i.e. all elements of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> are identified.</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>
                <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
              <fr:day>19</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-000U</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000U.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Biinverse">Biinverse</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000U.agda" type="external">erct-000U.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>A <html:em><html:strong>biinverse</html:strong></html:em> to a function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex> is defined to be a pair of a <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000Y.xml" title="Section-retraction pair" addr="forest://erct/erct-000Y" type="local">section</fr:link> and a <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000Y.xml" title="Section-retraction pair" addr="forest://erct/erct-000Y" type="local">retraction</fr:link> to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>. We will refer to a function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A\to  B]]></fr:tex> equipped with a biinverse as a <html:em><html:strong>biinvertible function</html:strong></html:em>.</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>
                <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
              <fr:day>19</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-000Y</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000Y.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Section-retraction pair">Section-retraction pair</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000Y.agda" type="external">erct-000Y.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s \colon  B \to  A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r \colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex> be a pair of maps. A homotopy <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[h \colon  r\circ  s \sim  1_{B}]]></fr:tex> exhibits <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s]]></fr:tex> as a <html:em><html:strong>section</html:strong></html:em> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r]]></fr:tex> as a <html:em><html:strong>retraction</html:strong></html:em> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s]]></fr:tex>. Together, 
 <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left \lparen s,r\right \rparen \mathclose {}]]></fr:tex>
 are referred to as a <html:em><html:strong>section-retraction pair</html:strong></html:em>.</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>
                <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
              <fr:day>19</fr:day>
            </fr:date>
            <fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-0015</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0015.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="The univalence principle for dependent functions">The univalence principle for dependent functions</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Axiom</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-0015.agda" type="external">erct-0015.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>The <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-004B.xml" title="Reflexive graph" addr="forest://erct/erct-004B" type="local">reflexive graph</fr:link> structure on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{Bx}]]></fr:tex> by <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0014.xml" title="Homotopy" addr="forest://erct/erct-0014" type="local">homotopy</fr:link> and <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0014.xml" title="Homotopy" addr="forest://erct/erct-0014" type="local">identity homotopies</fr:link> is <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0010.xml" title="Path object" addr="forest://erct/erct-0010" type="local">univalent</fr:link>.</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
      </fr:mainmatter>
